# One-shot BBF regen input scaffolds (staging files used during BBF-63+ regen scripts)
# These are tracked in container-only /tmp paths during regen; if they leak into the
# working tree, they should not be committed. Match prefix `_bbfN` and include
# the canonical "input" / "input.json" / ".json" patterns we use.
_bb*_input*.json
